        <scopecontent id="ref7">
            <head>Scope and Content</head>
            <p>The collection contains the original manuscripts of 
                <persname>Susan B. Aller</persname> as well as her collection of works by Scottish journalist, playwright, and author 
                <persname>J.M. Barrie</persname>.</p>
        </scopecontent>
